  <brief_title>Comparing Paroxetine and Duloxetine on Cardiovascular Measures</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study of the Effects of Paroxetine vs. Duloxetine on Heart Rate Variability and Autonomic Cardiovascular Control</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
